{"tid":1367883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12點 元朗國飛天南公祭","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:58:10.000Z","uid":18824,"like":335,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"5e621f9d8ef80cba8d78342394d917fe6e0b2341","tid":1367883,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"永遠懷念飛天南，元朗建國功不可沒，名流千古<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTFZnUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTFZnUF.jpg&h=d6f6c618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間：12時<br />\n地點：水邊圍 (詳細地點視乎現場情況)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">特別要感謝俾錢眾籌準備今次公勵嘅市民，已準備6位嘅花牌</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1. 何君妖<br />\n何家小雞陀衰家<br />\n妖言惑眾刁那媽<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2. 林鄭<br />\n自以為是好打得<br />\n出賣港人唔要得</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3. 飛天南<br />\n阿爺出錢你出命<br />\n死到臨頭唔知碇</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">4. 元朗國白衫軍<br />\n保家衛國假名儀<br />\n恐襲市民自作孽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n5. 盧偉聰<br />\n小氣一哥唔執法<br />\n包庇黑幫齊犯法<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">6. 鄧炳強<br />\n射殺學生無示警<br />\n精英警察變黑警</div><br />\n感謝標語創作嘅參加者<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已有物資:</span></div><br />\n1.溪錢<br />\n2.紙紮手錶<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">需要資源:</span></span></div><br />\n1.堂倌或堂倌服<br />\n2.大聲公大電池<br />\n3.元寶蠟燭嘅蠟燭<br />\n<br />\n堂倌請tg @yahowah"},{"pid":"c60b0ac02fcd99c90435fbf929aef646ba3e6d02","tid":1367883,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"6b62c1fc56efabe48142d39a9a5fcf5a0ca05d09","tid":1367883,"uid":5490,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"唔係無事咩？"},{"pid":"06622586ee611f872140d3619db4c1dcefe81491